import React from "react";
import SidebarMenu from 'react-bootstrap-sidebar-menu';

const Sidebar = () => {
    return (
        <>
        <SidebarMenu>
            <SidebarMenu.Header>
                <SidebarMenu.Brand>
                    icon
                </SidebarMenu.Brand>
                <SidebarMenu.Toggle/>
            </SidebarMenu.Header>

            <SidebarMenu.Body>
                <SidebarMenu.Nav>
                    <SidebarMenu.Nav.Link>
                        <SidebarMenu.Nav.Icon>
                            {/* {icong} */}
                        </SidebarMenu.Nav.Icon>
                    </SidebarMenu.Nav.Link>
                </SidebarMenu.Nav>
            </SidebarMenu.Body>
        </SidebarMenu>
        </>
    )
}
